name: MEV Capital Usual Boosted USDT
description: The Usual Boosted USDT Morpho vault curated by MEV Capital is dedicated to providing capital to Usual protocol markets. It gives access to extra incentives from Usual to boost the USDT APR for borrowers. Morpho Vaults are curated lending vaults that can allocate deposits to any number of Morpho Markets. Each vault is customizable and has a different risk profile. Curators are independent, third-party risk experts who use their expertise to offer various Morpho Vaults.
